<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Annasetu - Bridge Between Food & Hunger</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      overflow-x:hidden;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
      background: #f9f9f9;
      color:#333;
    }
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      justify-content:center;
      align-items:center;
      text-align:center;
      padding:2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #ffffff, #e0f7e0, #fff7e0);
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size:4rem;
      color:#28a745;
      margin-bottom:0.5rem;
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
    }
    .hero p {
      font-size:1.5rem;
      color:#ff8800;
      margin-bottom:2rem;
      animation: fadeIn 3s ease-in-out;
    }
    .login-btn {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #28a745, #ff8800);
      color: #fff;
      padding:1rem 2rem;
      font-size:1.25rem;
      border:none;
      border-radius:50px;
      cursor:pointer;
      text-decoration:none;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      animation: pulse 2s infinite;
    }
    .login-btn:hover {
      transform: scale(1.1);
      box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(255,136,0,0.6),0 0 20px rgba(40,167,69,0.6);
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%,100%{transform:scale(1);}
      50%{transform:scale(1.05);}
    }
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {opacity:0; transform:translateY(20px);}
      to {opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}
    }
    .quotes {
      margin-top:2rem;
      font-size:1.2rem;
      color:#333;
      animation: fadeIn 4s ease-in-out;
    }
    .quotes span { display:block; margin:0.5rem 0; }
    .shape {
      position:absolute;
      opacity:0.25;
      border-radius:50%;
      animation: float 20s infinite ease-in-out alternate;
    }
    .circle1{width:150px;height:150px;background:#28a745;top:10%;left:10%;}
    .circle2{width:120px;height:120px;background:#ff8800;top:30%;left:80%;}
    .circle3{width:100px;height:100px;background:#ffffff;top:60%;left:40%;}
    @keyframes float {
      0%{transform:translateY(0) rotate(0deg);}
      50%{transform:translateY(-50px) rotate(45deg);}
      100%{transform:translateY(0) rotate(360deg);}
    }
    section {
      padding:4rem 2rem;
      max-width:1200px;
      margin:auto;
    }
    .about, .how {
      border-radius:20px;
      padding:4rem 2rem;
      margin-bottom:2rem;
    }
    .about { background:#28a745; color:white; }
    .how { background:#ff88009b; color:white; }
    h2{ font-size:2.5rem; margin-bottom:1rem; }
    p{ font-size:1.2rem; line-height:1.6; }
    footer{
      text-align:center;
      padding:2rem;
      background:#1a46b7;
      color:white;
    }
    @media(max-width:768px){
      .hero h1{font-size:3rem;}
      .hero p{font-size:1.2rem;}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="shape circle1"></div>
    <div class="shape circle2"></div>
    <div class="shape circle3"></div>
    <h1>Annasetu</h1>
    <p>Bridge Between Food & Hunger</p>
    <a href="/login" class="login-btn">Go to Login</a>
    <div class="quotes">
      <span>"No one should sleep hungry."</span>
      <span>"Share your food, spread happiness."</span>
      <span>"One plate can change a life."</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="about">
    <h2>About Annasetu</h2>
    <p>Our mission is to connect food donors with those in need, reducing hunger and food waste simultaneously. Everyone deserves a meal.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="how">
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p>Receivers submit food requests, donors see them in real-time, and can donate. Once the donation is confirmed, the request is fulfilled. Simple, fast, impactful.</p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Annasetu. All Rights Reserved.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
